The book about the topic is available on the link. [https://www.intechopen.com/books/2746]
Author: Shigeaki Sakurai
Title: Theory and Applications for Advanced Text Mining

We live in digital world with ton of data. Text is one of data where we can everywhere in online. From the text, we can get plenty of useful data such as predicting people's opinion on some topic.
and we can even predict market values such as stocks by analyzing text data.

In this book, the author will introduce about the text mining techniques what we can apply for the real text mining problem.
